citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 11:29am on
03/04/2014.
The licensee later contacted the APHIS VMO to discuss reasons for not being home for the inspection and to
update contact information for future inspections.
Exit interview was conducted by telephone with the licensee.
